{"2620020": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Ash and Tor: Yuma's Quest", "steam_appid": 2620020, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "dlc": [3045610], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索地牢並嘗試找到並拯救<strong>尤瑪女王</strong>...但等等：這幾乎是一個不可能的地牢。 為什麼？ 因為說起來很容易：你必須同時移動兩個騎士！！！ 你準備好在不死的情況下找到並拯救大量女孩了嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620020/extras/b9a66927516ada218d1d16765e185282.poster.avif?t=1759582817\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620020/extras/b9a66927516ada218d1d16765e185282.webm?t=1759582817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620020/extras/b9a66927516ada218d1d16765e185282.mp4?t=1759582817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特徵：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有簡單解謎機制的即時動作遊戲（如 Roguelike）；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 個控制器/鍵盤讓玩家同時移動 2 個角色；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9種語言可選（義大利文、英文、法文、德文、西班牙文、日文、簡體中文、繁體中文、俄文）；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24個關卡、8 個休息區和 4 個 Boss；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30 個可用物品（透過獲勝即可解鎖），可讓您提升角色；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >96 名女孩需要在地牢中營救。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620020/extras/e8f465af8aeec34d58e0ac2014db4ec1.poster.avif?t=1759582817\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620020/extras/e8f465af8aeec34d58e0ac2014db4ec1.webm